		<updated>2015-12-28T15:32:52Z</updated>
		<published>2015-12-28T15:32:52Z</published>
		<content type="html" xml:base="/index.php/management/how-i-hire-developers/#comment-4850987"><![CDATA[<p>The Technical Screen has basically become an industry in it&#8217;s own right, with <a href="http://www.testdome.com/" rel="nofollow">coding test platforms like TestDome</a> popping up. Which is not a bad thing. It makes it easier to filter out the bad apples. It just goes to show how important this step is.</p>
]]></content>
		<thr:in-reply-to ref="/?p=4159" href="/index.php/management/how-i-hire-developers/" type="text/html" />
	</entry>
